  0109  C3D6F4        		JP		CpmBiosBaseAdrs + CpmBiosConIn   - CpmBiosEntry
  010C  C3DDF4        		JP		CpmBiosBaseAdrs + CpmBiosConOut  - CpmBiosEntry
  010F  C3E1F4        		JP		CpmBiosBaseAdrs + CpmBiosList    - CpmBiosEntry
  0112  C3E5F4        		JP		CpmBiosBaseAdrs + CpmBiosPunch   - CpmBiosEntry
  0115  C3E9F4        		JP		CpmBiosBaseAdrs + CpmBiosReader  - CpmBiosEntry
  0118  C3ECF4        		JP		CpmBiosBaseAdrs + CpmBiosHome    - CpmBiosEntry
  011B  C3F0F4        		JP		CpmBiosBaseAdrs + CpmBiosSelDsk  - CpmBiosEntry
